ext-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, 'lucida sans regular', 'lucida sans unicode', arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34,34,34); line-height: 1.8em;\">Writing: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t</span>Exposure<br />\n\tExposure means showing, usually bring into light what was not easily seen before. What does the exposure refer to? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: The exposure was amazing... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) long exposure of pictures taken of the night sky<br />\n\t2) exposure of high level corruption<br />\n\t3) exposure in the public eye brought fame<br />\n\t4) avoid exposure to the elements<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tIn the corner of his office, he placed a small bottle of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cologne\" target=\"_blank\">cologne</a> on the shelf, next to, but not too close to the window to minimize exposure to direct sunlight, with the cap loosely placed on top. Of course, he knew that without keeping the lid on tightly, the liquid in the container would evaporate, but that was the exact reason for him to do so. Shawn did not have the habit of wearing cologne. Since he received this sample bottle as a souvenir from a launch party he attended, he found he quite enjoy the fragrance.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167460837986/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p775089/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p775089\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777378/\">李宇春变身1700万黑天鹅：红毯造型惊艳老外</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777533/\">如何克服开口说英语的恐惧？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776440/\">关于学渣的6个陋习，学霸们不要进来！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777528/\">2016最受尊敬名人榜出炉：盖茨和朱莉获榜首</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771876/\">致有梦想的你：如何成为生活的赢家？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p775143/\">BBC模仿秀: 杀人魔状告政府胜诉</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777359/\">新虐狗利器：情侣拥抱连帽衫随时随地秀恩爱</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777643/\">卡特被砍傲骨贤妻季终2016哪些美剧说拜拜了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777655/\">有钱人的世界：围观欧洲皇室最奢华珠宝盘点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p777536/\">2010-2016公告牌十大金曲：居然它排名第1</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <